title: scroll_message_down()
brief: Scroll the current message down.
seealso: scroll_message_up
version: 0.08
----

<p>When in message-mode, set with <a href="global_mode.html">global_mode</a>, the user interface allows you to view a single message.</p>
<p>The <span class="tt">scroll_message_down()</span> function allows you to scroll the current message down, viewing any portion of the message which is off the screen.</p>
